The paper uses data from social media (Google+) to study migration patterns, which falls under the category of social media analysis (cs.SI). The paper also uses machine learning techniques to develop a model for predicting migration clusters, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.SD). The paper also touches upon topics such as network analysis (cs.CY), social networks (cs.SOC), and data mining (cs.DL).
